    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250690/extras/98064d8ca816bae0ccfb0d4035660f48.poster.avif?t=1729264109\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250690/extras/98064d8ca816bae0ccfb0d4035660f48.webm?t=1729264109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250690/extras/98064d8ca816bae0ccfb0d4035660f48.mp4?t=1729264109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250690/extras/4f6a434091bd776745b2b4a2db09ea57.avif?t=1729264109\" width=600 height=132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SkyStrikers</strong> is a fast-paced, high-skill VR competition where every move counts. With physics-driven mechanics and real-time positioning, you'll need precision and teamwork to succeed. Choose from unique suit classes, each with special abilities designed for offense, defense, or control, and work with your team to dominate the arena. Whether rocket-jumping across the field or timing the perfect strike, Sky Strikers delivers the intensity of real-world sports in a thrilling virtual experience!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250690/extras/90df8c3d92d90cdac8ade4f62de8dbc1.poster.avif?t=1729264109\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250690/extras/90df8c3d92d90cdac8ade4f62de8dbc1.webm?t=1729264109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250690/extras/90df8c3d92d90cdac8ade4f62de8dbc1.mp4?t=1729264109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250690/extras/7cca0ca35e5a46e09eed5cd3de251071.avif?t=1729264109\" width=600 height=132 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive VR Sports Action</strong>: Experience the intensity of competitive aerial sports in virtual reality, where every play requires precision and skill.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Social Hub for Multiplayer Fun</strong>: Meet up with friends in the <i>Sky Strikers</i> Social Hub, where up to 10 players can participate in casual games like Volleyball, The Floor is Lava, and HollowHoops.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250690/extras/7ba431693b5012c74de48c277fc885bc.avif?t=1729264109\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250690/extras_big/7ba431693b5012c74de48c277fc885bc.avif?t=1729264109 width=800 height=450 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ranked 3v3 Matchmaking</strong>: Test your skills in <i>Skyball</i> matches inside <i>The Dome</i>. Climb the leaderboards, earn your spot in the <i>Hall of Heroes</i>, and be immortalized as a top player.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250690/extras/6b3b540e8928f7252a6f5cfbc77c85da.avif?t=1729264109\" width=600 height=312 /></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique Classes &amp; Abilities</strong>: Choose from different suit classes, each offering distinct abilities like rocket boosters and game-changing moves to help your team win.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategic Team Play</strong>: Work together with your teammates, combining class abilities and tactics to outmaneuver your opponents.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Aerial Maneuvers</strong>: Master gravity-defying moves, soaring through the air to make the perfect play.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250690/extras/8dac52248db6d27cc6307a5d2f8692d7.poster.avif?t=1729264109\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250690/extras/8dac52248db6d27cc6307a5d2f8692d7.webm?t=1729264109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250690/extras/8dac52248db6d27cc6307a5d2f8692d7.mp4?t=1729264109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250690/extras/6e4a9e98dba1b671c9114c01c48d430f.avif?t=1729264109\" width=600 height=132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join our community on <strong>Discord</strong>, or follow us on <strong>YouTube</strong> to get the latest news about the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250690/extras/8194b4922c2d78699eefb0f6ff71ff8b.poster.avif?t=1729264109\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250690/extras/8194b4922c2d78699eefb0f6ff71ff8b.webm?t=1729264109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250690/extras/8194b4922c2d78699eefb0f6ff71ff8b.mp4?t=1729264109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250690/extras/221a466cd93b3d9343872eab6bb9b092.avif?t=1729264109\" width=600 height=81 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Chamber 8 Studio is a VR game development studio dedicated to creating immersive and high-quality virtual reality experiences. With a passion for innovative gameplay and pushing the boundaries of VR, Chamber 8 Studio brings competitive sports to life with Sky Strikers, a game designed to challenge players and redefine what it means to compete in virtual reality.</i></p>",
